Description: Implements the MOON Markov cohort model for simulating
    obesity prevalence, incremental health-care costs, and years of life
    lost in a Norwegian birth cohort over the life course. Originally
    described in Bjørnelv et al. (2021) <doi:10.1177/0272989X20971589>;
    this package is an R port and refactor of the Excel/VBA
    implementation.
